org.ros.gwt.client
Interface ROS.MessageListener

Enclosing class:
ROS
public static interface ROS.MessageListener

ROS.MessageListener is notified when a message is received from rosbridge. ROS.MessageListeners are registered/deregistered using ROS.addMessageListener(java.lang.String, org.ros.gwt.client.ROS.MessageListener) and ROS.removeMessageListener(java.lang.String, org.ros.gwt.client.ROS.MessageListener).
